description: The investigator of nightmare is faced with a woman who holds him captive , and tells him many stories , each of which is one analysis of Dylan's personality.
name: Labirinti di paura

description: The Randall family goes on vacation , but it, and even their mortal life, ends well before the start of the holiday . The only survivor is young Jimmy, but he finds himself in the world of the dead for an error . Dylan will be up to remedy this misconception with the help of Godfrey (" The Haunted House " , issue #30 ) from the "Inferno" and his daughter Windy, from the world of the living.
name: I vivi e i morti

description: Captain America: proud member of the Avengers, but a man out of time - frozen for decades and unaccustomed to modern life. Can the Sentinel of Liberty learn to fight alongside heroes 60 years younger than him? And why does Cap feel a strange connection to the man named Korvac? Ben McCool (Choker) brings you an epic tale ten centuries in the making! Collects Captain America & the Korvac Saga #1-4.
name: Captain America and the Korvac Saga

volume.name: Captain America and the Korvac Saga

description:
The mighty German battle-cruiser lay silent in the Atlantic fog, waiting, her guns loaded and ready. And straight into this trap a convoy of heavily-laden merchant ships was sailing.
On a radar screen the German Captain watched its progress with a grim smile. He was master of their fate and would spare not a single ship.

But there was a gleam of hope for the convoy - the gleam of the golden badge of the Royal Navy aboard one ship - a tiny ship. But crammed with British fighting courage

Originally Commando No.7.
name: The Ship They Couldn't Sink

description:
Everyone knew Ted Whitmore was yellow. Everything he did proved it. He even got himself and his men captured and put in a prison cage.

But then things began to happen - things that made his men stare in amazement and the enemy run for their lives!
name: Escape!

description:
During the three-year Korean War, a host of different nationalities were brought together to fight together under the United Nations flag. Generally they put their differences aside and did just that.

But one group of men thrown together by the conflict didn't look likely to be able to get along at alleven though their lives depended on it.
name: League of Nations

description:
A squad of British Royal Engineers are dropped behind the lines to halt German demolition work in occupied Italy. Unfortunately, they end up miles from their target, deep in the rugged mountains of Calabria.

To make matters worse, there's a Waffen SS unit on their tail - and they're caught in a violent feud between two warring Italian mountain clans!

The Italians will have put all their differences aside to fight alongside the British against the common enemybut can they?
name: Army of Bandits

description: Najah continues her mission in a small country ofAfrica, where a french politician plans to support a coup d'etat. There are official and convincing reasons, but the plan is to take over the oil resources and share the profits with amultinational company.
name: Opration Offshore

description: Najah starts her mission at Monaco GP, where somepeople pay their yachtswith weapon trafficking.Following these deals, Najah goes to Pakistan with the nephew of France's Prime Minister.
name: Missiles pour Islamabad

description: Najah is trapped in Afghanistan, among opium poppies and Taliban warlords. She continues to unveal international secret deals between mafias and west polticians.
name: Le pige afghan

description: Najah arrives to a violent atmosphere in Moscow. There is a fight for the power and the control of energetic resources.
name: O.P.A. sur le Kremlin

description: The russian army arrests Najah for fighting in the Chechen Republic. She is sentenced to death penalty and sent to a Gulag.
name: Destination Goulag

description: After escaping the gulag, Najah finds herself trapped among the chinese mafia. She has to make some quick decisions to stay alive and continue her mission.
name: Les dragons de Pkin

description:
Najah's secret identity is at risk and the warfor economic and poltic interests is intensifying.

This issue suppose the end of first season, and the outcome of Najah's mission.
name: Le prince rouge

description:
"What is the use of a book," thought Alice, "without pictures or conversations!"

Following up on the success of The Complete Dracula, and Sherlock Holmes, Dynamite presents The Complete Alice In Wonderland. In this All Ages adaptation, writers John Reppion and Leah Moore are joined by Erica Awano for an adventure down the rabbit hole as the present the complete opening chapter: Alice's Adventures in Wonderland! Features issues 1 and 2 of the Dynamite series!
name: Alice's Adventures
